<section class="section2">
    <div class="container clearfix">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12">
                <h2>Travelogists</h2>
                <div class="head-underline-s"> </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12">
                <!--<h4>Velvett Homestays. Don’t Just Visit. Belong.</h4>-->

                <p>
                    We are them.
                </p>
                <p>
                    We are not bloggers, nor are we travel content writers. We are that travel happy duo that seem to have lived your travel dreams.
                    Had the experiences you've read about on blogs or fancy travel journals.
                </p>
                <p>
                    We are a bunch of self taught / self proclaimed travelogists. Ready to share our magic formula with you and hoping to gain some insights from you too.
                    Spreading the love and joy of assimilating into a place vs. simply visiting. We don't just travel, we cover grounds. We don't just visit. We belong.
