                            <div class="text-center">
                                <p>Hi, I am Sagar.</p>
                                <p>
                                    ​One of the​ ​T​ravelogist​s​ at Velvett Homestays. My idea of travelling is to experience and ​create lifelong​​ ​memories all over the world.
                                    I haven’t been everywhere, but it’s on my list.
                                </p>
                                <p>
